	(text "Note on SMPS:\nThe SMPS uses a switching voltage regulator to increase \nthe efficiency of the STM32, but given the added complexity \nand relatively small gain in power efficiency (plus the \nrisk of the switching FETs latching in space), I dont think \nthis is necesarry."
